## Testing Contract

Issue #1: Title day-of-week must match <updated> date

```clojure
;; MUST return :day-of-week-mismatch error
(validate-entry {:title "Morning Brief: Thursday, June 19"
                 :updated "2026-06-19T00:00:00Z" ...})
;; June 19, 2026 is Friday!
```

## Boundaries

- Detects day names in any position in title
- Case insensitive matching
- Uses clj-time for day-of-week calculation

## PBT Coverage

- prop-mismatched-days-always-invalid (20 runs)
- prop-correct-days-no-day-error (20 runs)
